<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>{{name}} | Cristian Rodriguez</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/project.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="../assets/fav.png"/>

</head>

<body>
    <header class="NavBar">
        <div class="logo">
            <div class="image">
                <svg width="50" height="42" viewBox="0 0 50 42" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path
                        d="M41.624 2.83655L28.2816 15.9559C28.662 16.5426 28.9042 17.2313 28.9128 17.9795C28.9301 20.1052 27.192 21.8482 25.0389 21.8652C22.8771 21.8822 21.1045 20.1732 21.0872 18.0561C21.0785 17.2823 21.312 16.5596 21.7098 15.9474L8.37596 2.83655C4.56259 6.87524 2.24517 12.2913 2.29706 18.2261C2.40947 30.5292 12.6909 40.4517 25.2118 40.3411C37.7328 40.2306 47.824 30.1211 47.7029 17.8095C47.6511 12.0278 45.3423 6.77321 41.624 2.83655Z"
                        stroke-width="3" stroke-miterlimit="10" />
                    <path
                        d="M25.0303 10.9565C26.8202 10.9395 28.2556 9.50253 28.2383 7.74251C28.221 5.98249 26.7597 4.57107 24.9697 4.58807C23.1798 4.60508 21.7444 6.05051 21.7617 7.80202C21.779 9.56204 23.2403 10.9735 25.0303 10.9565Z"
                        stroke-width="3" stroke-miterlimit="10" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h1>
                <b>
                    Cristian
                </b>
                <br />
                Rodriguez
            </h1>
        </div>

        <nav id="mainmenu">
            <ul>
                <li data-menuanchor="The-Beginning"><a href="/#TheBeginning">The Beginning</a></li>
                <li  class="active" data-menuanchor="The-Projects"><a href="/#TheProjects">The projects</a></li>
                <li><a href="/AboutMe">About me</a></li>
                <li><a href="/Contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="Project">
        <div class="banner screen">
            <div class="banner__controler">
                <div class="prev">
                    <svg width="12" height="22" viewBox="0 0 12 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M11.5 21.5L1 11L11.5 0.5" stroke="black" />
                    </svg>

                </div>
                <div class="descriptors">
                    <h2 class="name">
                        {{name}}
                    </h2>
                    <p class="category">
                        {{category}}
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="next">
                    <svg width="13" height="22" viewBox="0 0 13 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M1 0.5L11.5 11L1 21.5" stroke="black" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="scroll_popper">
                <p>Watch more</p>
                <svg width="19" height="19" viewBox="0 0 19 19" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M2 2L9.5 9L17 2" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />
                    <path d="M2 9L9.5 16L17 9" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />
                </svg>

            </div>
            <div class="banner__mockup" style="background-image: url('{{bannermock}}');">
            </div>
        </div>

        {{#if id=='ice_cream'}}
        <div class="intro screen">
            <p class="text">
                {{introtextnormal}} <b>{{introtextbold}}</b>
            </p>
            <div class="image"  style="background-image: url('{{introimage}}');">

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="wave screen">
            <div class="waveback">
                <svg width="100%" viewBox="0 0 1152 256" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M0 76.8001H48C96 76.8001 192 76.8001 288 76.8001C384 76.8001 480 76.8001 576 68.2401C672 60.0001 768 42.4001 864 34.1601C960 25.6001 1056 25.6001 1104 25.6001H1152V256H1104C1056 256 960 256 864 256C768 256 672 256 576 256C480 256 384 256 288 256C192 256 96 256 48 256H0V76.8001Z"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="wavecontainer">
                <div class="text">
                    <p class="title">
                        How did it work?
                    </p>
                    <p class="body">
                        A trivia asked a series of questions to the user, the user answered them and an ice cream was assigned, according to they personality.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="mockup" style="background-image: url('../assets/projects/iceCream/wave.png');">

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image" style="background-image: url('../assets/projects/iceCream/trivia.png');">
            
        </div>
        <div class="textS">
            <p>
                The project was about the redesign of Ice Cream Nation’s website. It focused in a young target between 18 and 24 years, with the purpose to get more young people.
The trivia is selected by its engaging and its ease of sharing on social media.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="image" style="background-image: url('../assets/projects/iceCream/characters.png');">

        </div>
        <div class="title">
            <p>The characters</p>
        </div>
        <div class="textS">
            <p>Were selected vivid colors to attract people’s interest. The different colours and accesories were added to make it personanizable, the people answered a trivia and the app tell them.</p>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

    </div>
</body>

</html>